  <worksheets>
    <worksheet name='Energy ranking'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>Per-query energy ranking, by query length tier</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>194 (model × query length) data points from Jegham et al. environmental footprint snapshot. Models are sorted on the y-axis by mean per-query energy averaged across the three query lengths (ascending). Where a dot falls to the right or left of the prevailing curve in any panel, that horizontal displacement reveals the magnitude of its rank shift between tiers — the largest reshuffling happens in the middle of the distribution; the most efficient and the most expensive models stay roughly pinned. Per-tier energy spreads: 406×, 254×, 184× (short, medium, long). Four 2023-vintage models (GPT-3.5 Turbo, GPT-4, Llama 3 8B, Llama 3 70B) lack long-tier benchmarks and are absent from the long panel.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </caption>
      </layout-options>
      <table>
        <view>
          <datasources>
            <datasource caption='c2_model_energy' name='federated.1mldx7i07vmxij1gyr8ly1a4xbu1' />
          </datasources>
          <datasource-dependencies datasource='federated.1mldx7i07vmxij1gyr8ly1a4xbu1'>
            <column datatype='real' name='[Mean Combined Energy (Wh)]' role='measure' type='quantitative' />
            <column datatype='string' name='[Model]' role='dimension' type='nominal' />
            <column datatype='string' name='[Organization]' role='dimension' type='nominal' />
            <column datatype='integer' name='[Query Length]' role='measure' type='quantitative' />
            <column-instance column='[Mean Combined Energy (Wh)]' derivation='Avg' name='[avg:Mean Combined Energy (Wh):qk]' pivot='key' type='quantitative' />
            <column-instance column='[Query Length]' derivation='Avg' name='[avg:Query Length:qk]' pivot='key' type='quantitative' />
            <column-instance column='[Model]' derivation='None' name='[none:Model:nk]' pivot='key' type='nominal' />
            <column-instance column='[Organization]' derivation='None' name='[none:Organization:nk]' pivot='key' type='nominal' />
            <column-instance column='[tier]' derivation='None' name='[none:tier:nk]' pivot='key' type='nominal' />
            <column caption='Tier' datatype='string' name='[tier]' role='dimension' type='nominal' />
          </datasource-dependencies>
          <computed-sort column='[federated.1mldx7i07vmxij1gyr8ly1a4xbu1].[none:Model:nk]' direction='ASC' using='[federated.1mldx7i07vmxij1gyr8ly1a4xbu1].[avg:Mean Combined Energy (Wh):qk]' />
          <filter class='categorical' column='[federated.1mldx7i07vmxij1gyr8ly1a4xbu1].[none:Organization:nk]'>
            <groupfilter function='level-members' level='[none:Organization:nk]' user:ui-enumeration='all' user:ui-marker='enumerate' />
